Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:41.50,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,700)}{\pos(230,80)}第12回 不可思议的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是从今天开始的一个月里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要和大家一起学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必大家都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥友里惠大人是神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家不要太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用对我那么客气的啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂敢岂敢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是中学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙还是神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云可是非常尊重神仙的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐到位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出差？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定知道10月是神奈月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的神仙们都会这一个月期间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在出云举行集会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必出席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都要去出云吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学会比较省力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈不会同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是很重要的行事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两亲方面我会去说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宿和饮食方面协会也会安排好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一个月..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里为止的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在期中考试里出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好好的复习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们的学校进度还快..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是学习委员阿倍直人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被指名来照顾一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是转学生 又是同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再称呼的轻松点么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学级会规定了 对神仙是不能失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是神仙没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但主要的身份不是那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫我一桥或者友里惠什么的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在学级会讨论一下的

Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…校商店在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一楼的楼梯旁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大妈 给我两份肉夹面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒面面包 还要个奶油面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要插队嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 相当混乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要意思…那个 我要三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 炒面面包和奶油面包对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么面包都好啦…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神仙大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过恭敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都刻意关照着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道作为神仙的友里惠大人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但期中考试一定要考的啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个归这个 先不说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后请在校门口等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人来接您的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后教数学的小至就..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 那真是了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么关系的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是在害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惹神仙就不会遭天谴..吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会天谴什么的呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月…好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月 我家赤字是定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是变回原样而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为认真的神社 正常营业嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种生存方法已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道友里惠顺不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天..休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学去出云了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要出席神仙的集会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才会回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说下个月就回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找友里惠有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥同学不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得少了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 他刚刚说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说他在乎友里惠的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有意识到她的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 如果友里惠知道一定会高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 等很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约她看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来接您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说等你很久..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙大会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称神会的会场一眨眼就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的人是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然那些人也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁在说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是神仙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点——神会会场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上会来接您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别迷路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是前阵子的新人么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众神之中最后才出席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆子可真不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIAHIA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要上学..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一两个人迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会察觉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我在这里该做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去学习一些新人的心得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穷已经隐退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还挺喜欢你制造的不景气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说完全隐退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多算停业整顿吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见喽 又想干的时候记得告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神还是那么有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穷神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八岛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有弁天大人的演唱会..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就准备来打气..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人已经到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪鹿碟应该去迎接了

Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..是在新人研修吧

Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能多参加计划来提升神通力吧

Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加的话就能在这里敲印章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集满20个以上的话在最后一天会有微薄的礼品奉上

Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么解散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了呀 都不知道看哪个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从友里惠大人感兴趣的开始逛怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感兴趣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来想成为怎样的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得只要去找能为此学到东西的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的神仙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有点事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是追星 追星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下 再想想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先来一首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙迟到的话可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙不用上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在学级会讨论过了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定在班级里称一桥大人为友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥同学的多数顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫您友里惠大人可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还是有点生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢..谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组是由留在京都的近藤勇和芹泽鸭为中心建立的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护将军上京而从江户招募的浪人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(360,310,360,310)\fs26\bord0\shad0\1c&H000000&\fn宋体}只能女孩子看
