Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}汁粉:  将豆沙和糖水一起煮以后塞入饼或面团的甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新撰组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组在暗中维护着京都的治安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜伏在城市中..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在上课的时候传递奇怪的纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试范围超出那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能好好复习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教科书也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找不到人商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和神仙没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对中学生来说可是大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八岛大人去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找一下..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我在外面等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可以坐么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是死神么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛~~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太死气沉沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙如果不一直很开朗的话可不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了信神的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是中学生..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神仙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙不能有烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可不能“求神拜佛”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能靠的只有自己和..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁..弁天大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月过得还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人今天也要回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还有照顾不周的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必在最后赠与一些祝福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得和大家见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我胆子太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总想着和大家多说说话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是开不了口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键应该不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就作为既是神仙又是中学生的一桥友里惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家成为朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一桥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和友里惠大人成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年也请来我们的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想会称呼着友里惠来欢迎你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..这个能在学级会提前决定下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用决定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会赞成的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年一定要来哦 我们都期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:23:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友里惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.29,0:24:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是能一个人回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光惠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.94,0:24:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.01,0:24:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定一个人很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.35,0:24:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.63,0:24:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:24:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.85,0:24:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.36,0:25:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到了很多朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.52,0:26:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是神仙 也很期待圣诞节哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.23,0:26:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今年小祀预谋着开展
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.38,0:26:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神社为了神社而举行的神社活动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.00,0:26:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很激动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.75,0:26:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是『随心所欲』
